title: Spencer Nilsen - Architects of Change (1989)(FLAC)[image+cue]
description:
Ripped using Rubyripper from a CD purchased on Ebay. This album is basically out of print and as far as I could tell only available on youtube. This album predates Spencer's work on the Sega CD, and fans of his video game music (Ecco the Dolphin, Sonic CD) will likely enjoy this as well.


Artist	= Spencer Nilsen
Album	= Architects of Change
Year	= 1989
Genre	= New Age
Tracks	= 10

01 - Windows
02 - Spoken Once...
03 - Architects of Change
04 - Pyramids
05 - Spain By Horseback
06 - Rain In The Lowlands
07 - Church on Wally St.
08 - Paper House
09 - Healing The Dream
10 - Windows (reprise)


This torrent includes the album as a single FLAC file with a cue sheet. I have also uploaded a version with split tracks.
